ITV Tonight: Bargain Britain
In Britain we love a brilliant bargain and spend over a year of our lives seeking out the best possible deals. With wages lagging behind the rising costs of everyday life, we're all becoming more conscious of getting the most for our money. But what's the best route to a real bargain? Jonathan Maitland sets out to discover creative ways to get true value for money in Bargain Britain...
